{"tid":1081371,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"港鐵按機制今年可加價3.3%","createTime":"2019-03-28T08:55:33.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-28T17:17:52.000Z","uid":1121,"like":0,"dislike":22,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"6e8ed26bf5c3b43153311d64d9b63bf1fe111a03","tid":1081371,"uid":1121,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-28T08:55:33.000Z","msg":"港鐵(00066)根據可加可減機制，今年票價可加3.3%。<br />\n<br />\n政府最新公布去年12月運輸業名義工資指數按年升5.9%，加上同期通脹率2.5%，根據票價調整機制，兩者相加除二，計及港鐵承諾的0.6%的票價調整減幅，今年港鐵票價加幅3.6%，但觸發封頂機制，因此加幅限於3.3%。"},{"pid":"712e3061601c9ee203cff3d23dc088e5cd63d4cb","tid":1081371,"uid":1121,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-28T08:56:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/2567234/org/e8159d70aa3e9b93adffd3bff2b344c6.jpg/z9dpA96P0LZEWSfnEsZ6T1pRbJ55cxi6v6wikb-sIpE?v=w1920\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F2567234%2Forg%2Fe8159d70aa3e9b93adffd3bff2b344c6.jpg%2Fz9dpA96P0LZEWSfnEsZ6T1pRbJ55cxi6v6wikb-sIpE%3Fv%3Dw1920&h=172d3daa&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"0524241c67bf457dbeebdfbcfbdcebdb263966dd","tid":1081371,"uid":1550,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-28T08:56:33.000Z","msg":"可加可減真係一個笑話"},{"pid":"81e41b432075e67f9fe7bb3b0af2a6309c39ada5","tid":1081371,"uid":1121,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-28T08:58:29.000Z","msg":"炒車 壞車都照加<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d78720c39e8d51f6e2dfe6a93eaf81e5971f3221","tid":1081371,"uid":1121,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-28T08:59:48.000Z","msg":"政府統計處公布去年第四季運輸業名義工資指數為5.9%，連同統計署早前公布去年12月的通脹率為2.5%，按港鐵票價可加可減機制運算後，去年盈利達160億元、近年接連爆發工程醜聞及嚴重列車事故的港鐵，6月起將可加價3.3%。<br />\n<br />\n去年12月運輸業名義工資指數按年升5.9%，連同統計處早前公布的去年12月通脹率按年升2.5%，以及生產力因素和「額外扣減」因素，按機制方程式運算後，今年得出結果為3.6%。<br />\n<br />\n不過，按現行港鐵票價可加可減機制下設立的「封頂機制」，港鐵加幅不能超出去年第四季家庭月入中位數的按年變幅，當中統計處早前已公布去年第四季家庭月入中位數按年增加3.3%，即無論港鐵在機制運算下的結果如何，加幅須於3.3%「封頂」。<br />\n<br />\n今次是可加可減機制運作以來，首次觸及「封頂機制」。雖然在3.3%「封頂」，但今次加幅仍較上次的3.14%為高。<br />\n<br />\n現時由荃灣往金鐘的八達通車費為14.7元，港鐵加價3.3%後，預料新票價需要15.2元；由屯門往中環的八達通車費，亦會由現時27.5元，增加至28.4元。<br />\n<br />\n港鐵曾承諾自2017年起的未來6年內，每年有6個月提供每程八達通車費九七折優惠。港鐵料於5月公布今年的車費優惠。"},{"pid":"42c367b1b223ff2ca8f5c6fc55bdd8ee322f49d9","tid":1081371,"uid":78791,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-03-28T09:00:15.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"fc2a9c226a731c8cbeaea21743db150d36dcc035","tid":1081371,"uid":97776,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-28T09:00:57.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">可加</span><span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">可減</span>"},{"pid":"702599e3a1038e49ee18ca45db4f835658b864c7","tid":1081371,"uid":86509,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"42c367b1b223ff2ca8f5c6fc55bdd8ee322f49d9","tid":1081371,"uid":78791,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-03-28T09:00:15.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-28T09:00:58.000Z","msg":"奶共張五常都要行開一邊<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fd6c3922bd909c6c9034ede6736a6eb1eba0ed6f","tid":1081371,"uid":1121,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-28T09:03:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8572c75217fb73ca5dbb1cc352d6dfc70c75765c","tid":1081371,"uid":1121,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-28T09:04:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3fyF8Q4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3fyF8Q4.png&h=c9167a9d&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"1e991c0796726886cf3f61646ffef492082ff47f","tid":1081371,"uid":241794,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"42c367b1b223ff2ca8f5c6fc55bdd8ee322f49d9","tid":1081371,"uid":78791,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy"